text.tspan: I believe that the TTC needs to improve in some areas.
Waiting a long time for buses and realize that they
are crowded is a frustrating morning experience...
Jessica is a Graphic Designer working on an Advertising company in Toronto.
During the week she spends a great deal of time commuting and using the TTC
services. Jessica does not own a car and relies on public transportation to move
around the city. On weekends she enjoys hanging out with her friends and
attending music / food festivals & attractions across Toronto.
Have a comfortable experience during her commute
Reduce her stress due to TTC delays and crowded vehicles
Improve her skills and grow professionally
Arriving late at work because of TTC problems
Having to wait a long time for an available bus
